奧斯爾於季前的[[酋長盃|酋長盃]]對陣[[里昂足球會|里昂]]的賽事後，再次獲得雲加的稱讚，認為他尚未到達自己的高峰<ref>{{en}}{{cite web |url=https://uk.eurosport.yahoo.com/news/premier-league-arsene-wenger-backs-mesut-ozil-shine-182631092--sow.html |title=Premier League – Arsene Wenger backs Mesut Ozil to shine |date=2015-05-25 |work=Yahoo Eurosport UK |accessdate=2015-07-27 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20160717060517/https://uk.eurosport.yahoo.com/news/premier-league-arsene-wenger-backs-mesut-ozil-shine-182631092--sow.html |archivedate=2016-07-17 }}</ref>。他於[[英格蘭社區盾|英格蘭社區盾]]對陣[[車路士足球會|車路士]]的賽事以及英超首戰對陣[[韋斯咸足球會|韋斯咸]]的賽事中皆有上陣。其中在社區盾的賽事中，以1比0擊敗車路士贏得冠軍<ref>{{en}}{{cite news|url=http://www.theguardian.com/football/2015/aug/09/arsenal-west-ham-premier-league-match-report|title=West Ham capitalise on Petr Cech's debut errors to stun nervy Arsenal|date=2015-08-10|work=The Guardian|access-date=2015-10-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151027091553/http://www.theguardian.com/football/2015/aug/09/arsenal-west-ham-premier-league-match-report|archive-date=2015-10-27|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2015年10月4日，奧斯爾於對陣[[曼聯|曼聯]]時於十二碼點附近射入本季首個入球。在這入球前，他亦在第6分鐘時交出助攻給山齊士，帶領阿仙奴大勝3比0<ref>{{en}}{{cite news|url=http://www.bbc.com/sport/0/football/34372498|title=Arsenal 3–0 Man Utd|work=BBC|accessdate=2015-10-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151005010545/http://www.bbc.com/sport/0/football/34372498|archive-date=2015-10-05|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在兩星期後對陣[[屈福特足球會|屈福特]]的比賽中，他貢獻2次助攻給山齊士和基奧特，並獲得全場最佳球員的獎項<ref>{{en}}{{cite web|url= http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/live/football/34214347|title= Premier League: FT Watford 0–3 Arsenal – BBC Sport|work= BBC Sport|accessdate= 2015-10-09|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20151020010700/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/live/football/34214347|archive-date= 2015-10-20|dead-url= no}}</ref><ref>{{en}}{{cite web|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/34493696|title=BBC Sport – Watford 0–3 Arsenal|author=Saj Chowdhury|work=BBC Sport|accessdate=2015-10-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151018210903/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/34493696|archive-date=2015-10-18|dead-url=no}}</ref>。3天後，他在歐聯分組賽對陣[[拜仁慕尼黑足球會|拜仁慕尼黑]]的比賽中，射入鎖定勝局的一球<ref>{{en}}{{cite news|url=http://www.theguardian.com/football/blog/2015/oct/21/arsenal-bayern-munich-champions-league-mesut-ozil|title=Mesut Özil greases the cogs as Arsenal twist and turn to put Bayern in a spin|date=2015-10-21|work=The Guardian|access-date=2015-10-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151021212054/http://www.theguardian.com/football/blog/2015/oct/21/arsenal-bayern-munich-champions-league-mesut-ozil|archive-date=2015-10-21|dead-url=no}}</ref>。於[[北倫敦打吡|北倫敦打吡]]交出助攻給[[基蘭·基比斯|基比斯]]後，他成為英超首位連續6場比賽都能交出助攻的球員，其後更把紀錄增加至7場<ref>{{en}}{{cite news|title=Mesut Ozil: Arsenal playmaker makes history in Tottenham draw by becoming first player to assist in six consecutive Premier League games|url=http://www.independent.co.uk/sport/football/premier-league/mesut-ozil-arsenal-playmaker-makes-history-in-tottenham-draw-by-becoming-first-player-to-assist-in-a6726421.html|accessdate=2015-11-08|work=The Independent|date=2015-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151109074950/http://www.independent.co.uk/sport/football/premier-league/mesut-ozil-arsenal-playmaker-makes-history-in-tottenham-draw-by-becoming-first-player-to-assist-in-a6726421.html|archive-date=2015-11-09|dead-url=no}}</ref>。奧斯爾在歐聯對陣[[薩格勒布戴拿模|薩格勒布戴拿模]]和在英超對陣[[諾域治足球會|諾域治]]時皆有進帳<ref>{{en}}{{cite web|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/34892626|title=BBC Sport – Arsenal 3–0 Dinamo Zagreb|work=BBC Sport|accessdate=2015-11-30|author=Phil McNulty|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151128041930/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/34892626|archive-date=2015-11-28|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{en}}{{cite web|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/34893429|title=BBC Sport – Norwich City 1–1 Arsenal|work=BBC Sport|accessdate=2015-11-30|author=James Gheerbrant|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151129220310/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/34893429|archive-date=2015-11-29|dead-url=no}}</ref>，並在其後對陣[[阿士東維拉|阿士東維拉]]、[[曼城|曼城]]及[[新特蘭足球會|新特蘭]]的3場比賽中，交出4次助攻。2015年12月28日，在對陣[[般尼茅夫足球會|般尼茅夫]]的比賽中，奧斯爾創下英超單場創造機會紀錄，創造9次入球機會，收獲1個助攻<ref>{{en}}{{cite news |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/35148189 |title=Arsenal 2–0 Bournemouth |work=BBC Sport |publisher=BBC |date=2015-12-28 |accessdate=2016-01-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160102141714/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/35148189 |archive-date=2016-01-02 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{en}}{{cite news|title=Mesut Ozil in a league of his own as Arsenal beat Bournemouth|url=http://www.skysports.com/football/news/15118/10113153/mesut-ozil-in-a-league-of-his-own-as-arsenal-beat-bournemouth|accessdate=2015-12-29|work=Sky Sports|publisher=Sky Sports|date=2015-12-28|last1=Wright|first1=Nick|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151228223319/http://www.skysports.com/football/news/15118/10113153/mesut-ozil-in-a-league-of-his-own-as-arsenal-beat-bournemouth|archive-date=2015-12-28|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在稍後對[[修咸頓足球會|修咸頓]]的比賽中，更創造10次入球機會，可惜阿仙奴只能以0比0完成比賽，連續3場賽事皆沒法入球，聯賽排名下跌至第4名<ref>{{en}}{{cite news |url=http://metro.co.uk/2016/02/03/stats-show-arsenal-need-new-striker-after-0-0-draw-despite-mesut-ozil-creating-record-amount-of-chances-5659784/ |title=Stats show Arsenal need new striker after 0–0 draw despite Mesut Ozil creating record amount of chances |publisher=Metro |date=2016-02-03 |accessdate=2016-02-11 |author=Alex Brodie |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160206175940/http://metro.co.uk/2016/02/03/stats-show-arsenal-need-new-striker-after-0-0-draw-despite-mesut-ozil-creating-record-amount-of-chances-5659784/ |archive-date=2016-02-06 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2016年1月24日，奧斯爾替阿仙奴第100次上陣，可惜該場比賽主場以1比0不敵[[車路士足球會|車路士]]<ref>{{en}}{{cite news|url=http://www.turkish-football.com/mesut-ozil-loses-100th-game-for-arsenal-against-chelsea/|title=Mesut Ozil loses 100th game for Arsenal against Chelsea|publisher=Turkish Football|date=2016-01-25|accessdate=2016-01-25|author=Emre Sarigul|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160202133901/http://www.turkish-football.com/mesut-ozil-loses-100th-game-for-arsenal-against-chelsea/|archive-date=2016-02-02|dead-url=no}}</ref>。他其後於2月7日對陣般尼茅夫的比賽中，終結阿仙奴的入球荒<ref>{{en}}{{cite news |url=http://www.bbc.com/sport/football/35453143 |title=Arsenal scored twice in 88 first-half seconds to overwhelm Bournemouth and move level on points with second-placed Tottenham |publisher=BBC Sport |date=2016-02-07 |accessdate=2016-02-11 |author=Marc Higginson |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160210124314/http://www.bbc.com/sport/football/35453143 |archive-date=2016-02-10 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，並於一星期後對陣[[李斯特城足球會|李斯特城]]的比賽中，於補時階段交出本賽季第17次助攻予[[丹尼·维尔贝克|维尔贝克]]，以2比1絕殺李斯特城<ref>{{en}}{{cite news|url=http://www.theguardian.com/football/2016/feb/14/arsenal-leicester-city-premier-league-match-report|title=Danny Welbeck's last-gasp effort gives Arsenal win over 10-man Leicester|publisher=The Guardian|date=2016-02-14|accessdate=2016-02-14|author=Barney Ronay|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160214184022/http://www.theguardian.com/football/2016/feb/14/arsenal-leicester-city-premier-league-match-report|archive-date=2016-02-14|dead-url=no}}</ref>。奧斯爾於歐聯16強兩回合對陣[[巴塞隆拿足球會|巴塞隆拿]]的賽事，以及聯賽不敵曼聯3比2的賽事中皆有上陣，其中在對陣曼聯的比賽中，交出1入球1助攻<ref>{{en}}{{cite news|url=http://www.theguardian.com/football/2016/mar/16/barcelona-arsenal-champions-league-match-report|title=Luis Suárez acrobatics end Arsenal's unlikely resistance at Barcelona|publisher=The Guardian|date=2016-03-16|accessdate=2016-03-19|author=Sid Lowe|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160319004041/http://www.theguardian.com/football/2016/mar/16/barcelona-arsenal-champions-league-match-report|archive-date=2016-03-19|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{en}}{{cite news|url=http://www.theguardian.com/football/2016/feb/28/manchester-united-arsenal-premier-league-match-report|title=Marcus Rashford's double for Manchester United deflates Arsenal hopes|publisher=The Guardian|date=2016-02-28|accessdate=2016-02-28|author=Jamie Jackson|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160228195744/http://www.theguardian.com/football/2016/feb/28/manchester-united-arsenal-premier-league-match-report|archive-date=2016-02-28|dead-url=no}}</ref>。於對陣屈福特的足總盃8強賽事中，奧斯爾以後腳交出助攻給[[丹尼·维尔贝克|维尔贝克]]追近比數，可惜仍以2比1落敗，無緣足總盃冠軍。於本季最後一場聯賽中，奧斯爾交出第19次聯賽助攻給[[奥利弗·吉鲁|吉鲁]]，協助阿仙奴大勝4比0<ref>{{en}}{{cite news |url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/football/2016/05/15/arsenal-4-aston-villa-0-hosts-clinch-unlikely-st-totteringham-da/ |title=Arsenal 4 Aston Villa 0: Hosts clinch unlikely St Totteringham's Day as Olivier Giroud grabs hat-trick |publisher=The Telegraph |date=2016-05-15 |accessdate=2016-05-15 |author=Jeremy Wilson |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160518013447/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/football/2016/05/15/arsenal-4-aston-villa-0-hosts-clinch-unlikely-st-totteringham-da/ |archive-date=2016-05-18 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

奧斯爾今季有19次英超助攻，成為聯賽助攻王，可是差1次助攻才追平[[蒂埃里·亨利|亨利]]在2002-03賽季交出20次助攻的記錄。全季，奧斯爾在各項賽事攻入8球，並助攻20次，並贏得阿仙奴最佳球員<ref>{{en}}{{cite news|url=http://www.espnfc.com/player/84775/mesut-ozil?season=2015|title=Mesut Özil complete stats for 2015/16 season|date=2016-05-15|accessdate=2016-05-15|work=espnfc.com|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160611061956/http://www.espnfc.com/player/84775/mesut-ozil?season=2015|archive-date=2016-06-11|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{en}}{{cite news|url=http://www.espnfc.us/arsenal/story/2876662/mesut-ozil-named-arsenals-player-of-the-season-by-fans|title=Mesut Özil complete stats for 2015/16 season|date=2016-05-20|accessdate=2016-06-11|work=espnfc.com|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160529020339/http://www.espnfc.us/arsenal/story/2876662/mesut-ozil-named-arsenals-player-of-the-season-by-fans|archive-date=2016-05-29|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

====2016–17賽季 ====
奧斯爾為[[德國國家足球隊|德國國家足球隊]]出陣[[2016年歐洲國家盃|2016年歐洲國家盃]]後，缺陣了聯賽首戰對陣[[利物浦足球會|利物浦]]的比賽。他於8月27日上陣對陣[[沃特福德足球俱乐部|沃特福德]]的賽事，並以頭鎚攻入1球，協助球隊以3比1勝出比賽<ref>{{en}}{{cite news|title=Watford 1–3 Arsenal – BBC Sport|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/37139688|accessdate=2016-08-27|work=BBC Sport|date=2016-08-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160827072351/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/37139688|archive-date=2016-08-27|dead-url=no}}</ref>。10月19日對陣[[拉茲格勒盧多戈雷茨足球俱樂部|盧多格德斯]]的[[歐聯|歐聯]]比賽中，他交出1次助攻給[[西奥·沃尔科特|沃尔科特]]，其後再上演[[帽子戲法|帽子戲法]]，協助球隊大勝6比0<ref>{{en}}{{cite news|title=Arsenal 6–0 Ludogorets|url=http://www.skysports.com/football/arsenal-vs-ludogorets/366885|accessdate=2016-10-19|work=Sky Sports|date=2016-10-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161020172923/http://www.skysports.com/football/arsenal-vs-ludogorets/366885|archive-date=2016-10-20|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

====2017-18赛季====
厄齐尔在他的合同的最后一年进入了2017-18赛季，刚开始很挣扎，膝盖炎症不时作痛。他在10月22日以5-2击败[[埃弗顿|埃弗顿]]的比赛中贡献了一个进球和助攻，并在一周后主场战胜[[斯旺西城|斯旺西城]]的比赛中贡献了另一次助攻。<ref>{{en}}{{cite news|title=Everton 2-5 Arsenal – BBC Sport|url=https://www.bbc.com/sport/football/41625741|accessdate=2017-10-22|work=BBC Sport|date=2017-10-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171022121529/http://www.bbc.com/sport/football/41625741|archive-date=2017-10-22|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{en}}{{cite news|title=Arsenal 2-1 Swansea City – BBC Sport|url=https://www.bbc.com/sport/football/41703866|accessdate=2017-10-28|work=BBC Sport|date=2017-10-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171029041112/http://www.bbc.com/sport/football/41703866|archive-date=2017-10-29|dead-url=no}}</ref>在创造了第一个进球后，他在11月18日在[[北伦敦德比|北伦敦德比]]中的表现受到了极大的赞扬。<ref>{{en}}{{cite news|title=Arsenal 2-0 Tottenham Hotspur – BBC Sport|url=https://www.bbc.com/sport/football/41951916|accessdate=2017-11-18|work=BBC Sport|date=2017-11-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171118063424/http://www.bbc.com/sport/football/41951916|archive-date=2017-11-18|dead-url=no}}</ref>然后，他在5比0击败[[哈德斯菲尔德|哈德斯菲尔德]]的比赛中贡献进球和两个助攻，并在11月末背靠背对阵[[西汉姆联|西汉姆联]]队的比赛中进球，帮助队伍获胜，然后在12月末以3比3战平[[利物浦|利物浦]]的比赛中取得了亮眼的表现。<ref>{{en}}{{cite news|title=Arsenal 5-0 Huddersfield Town – BBC Sport|url=https://www.bbc.com/sport/football/42075942|accessdate=2017-11-29|work=BBC Sport|date=2017-11-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171129015825/http://www.bbc.com/sport/football/42075942|archive-date=2017-11-29|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{en}}{{cite news|title=Arsenal 3-3 Liverpool – BBC Sport|url=https://www.bbc.com/sport/football/42362392|accessdate=2017-12-22|work=BBC Sport|date=2017-12-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171222010916/http://www.bbc.com/sport/football/42362392|archive-date=2017-12-22|dead-url=no}}</ref>

在进入1月份，他的合同还有6个月，这将允许他与任何俱乐部进行合同到期前的谈判，厄齐尔贡献助攻帮助球队赢得了[[水晶宫|水晶宫]]，并在一月30日负于[[斯旺西城|斯旺西城]]的比赛中贡献一次助攻。<ref>{{en}}{{cite news|title=Arsenal 4-1 Crystal City – BBC Sport|url=https://www.bbc.com/sport/football/42672226|accessdate=2018-01-20|work=BBC Sport|date=2018-01-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180120080920/http://www.bbc.com/sport/football/42672226|archive-date=2018-01-20|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{en}}{{cite news|title=Swansea City 3-1 Arsenal – BBC Sport|url=https://www.bbc.com/sport/football/42784104|accessdate=2018-01-30|work=BBC Sport|date=2018-01-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180130061323/http://www.bbc.com/sport/football/42784104|archive-date=2018-01-30|dead-url=no}}</ref>一天后，他与俱乐部签订了为期三年的延期协议，并将其签约至2021年。<ref name="#1">{{en}}{{cite news|title=Mesut Ozil: Arsenal midfielder signs new contract until 2021 - BBC Sport|url=https://www.bbc.com/sport/football/42885533|accessdate=2018-01-31|work=BBC Sport|date=2018-01-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180201081405/http://www.bbc.com/sport/football/42885533|archive-date=2018-02-01|dead-url=no}}</ref>据报道，他的薪水每周增加了一倍多达到35万英镑，使他成为阿森纳历史上收入最高的球员。<ref>{{en}}{{cite news|title=Wenger: Paying Ozil mega salary was 'cheapest option' for Arsenal - ESPN|url=http://www.espn.co.uk/football/arsenal/story/3369152/arsene-wenger-paying-mesut-ozil-mega-salary-was-cheapest-option-for-arsenal|accessdate=2018-02-03|work=ESPN|date=2018-02-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180206131448/http://www.espn.co.uk/football/arsenal/story/3369152/arsene-wenger-paying-mesut-ozil-mega-salary-was-cheapest-option-for-arsenal|archive-date=2018-02-06|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{en}}{{cite news|title=Mesut Ozil agrees new £350,000-a-week deal to become Arsenal's highest paid player - The Telegraph|url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/football/2018/01/31/mesut-ozil-signs-new-350000-a-week-deal-become-arsenals-highest|accessdate=2018-01-31|work=The Telegraph|date=2018-01-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180131131504/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/football/2018/01/31/mesut-ozil-signs-new-350000-a-week-deal-become-arsenals-highest/|archive-date=2018-01-31|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="#1"/>

2月2日，厄齐尔在欧罗巴联赛对阵[[厄斯特松德|厄斯特松德]]的首轮淘汰赛中以一脚冷静推射取得进球。<ref>{{en}}{{cite news|title=Europa League Highlights: Östersunds 0-3 Arsenal|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pUfGHgPNB3w|accessdate=2018-02-15|work=BT Sport|date=2018-02-15|archive-date=2020-05-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200501020905/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pUfGHgPNB3w&gl=US&hl=en|dead-url=no}}</ref>并在下一轮对阵[[AC米兰|AC米兰]]的比赛中获得助攻。 <ref>{{en}}{{cite news|title=Europa League Highlights: AC Milan 0-2 Arsenal|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IIMM04aOarU|accessdate=2018-03-08|work=BT Sport|date=2018-03-08|archive-date=2018-03-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180309061502/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IIMM04aOarU&gl=US&hl=en|dead-url=no}}</ref>3月11日，厄齐尔在他的第50次英超联赛上贡献助攻，帮助球队以3比0击败[[沃特福德足球俱乐部|沃特福德]]。这个助攻使他成为了英超比赛中最快达到50次助攻的球员，在他的第141次出场中实现并打破了以前由[[坎通纳|坎通纳]]所保持的纪录。<ref>{{en}}{{cite news|title=Mesut Ozil brings up 50 Premier League assists in record time - Nick Wright|url=https://www.skysports.com/football/news/11670/11286094/mesut-ozil-brings-up-50-premier-league-assists-in-record-time|accessdate=2018-03-12|work=Sky Sports|date=2018-03-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180311194244/http://www.skysports.com/football/news/11670/11286094/mesut-ozil-brings-up-50-premier-league-assists-in-record-time|archive-date=2018-03-11|dead-url=no}}</ref>他于4月5日在对阵[[莫斯科中央陆军|莫斯科中央陆军]]的比赛中上演了助攻帽子戏法，继续他在欧罗巴联赛中的表现。<ref>{{en}}{{cite news|title=Arsenal 4-1 CSKA Moscow: Europa League highlights (Ramsey, Lacazette goals)|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=q-NYwUvw-bA|accessdate=2018-04-05|work=BT Sport|date=2018-04-05|archive-date=2018-04-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180406091157/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=q-NYwUvw-bA&gl=US&hl=en|dead-url=no}}</ref>虽然持续的伤病使他没有办法参加俱乐部本赛季的最后几场比赛，然而厄齐尔在35场比赛中以5球和13次助攻结束了他在阿森纳的第五个赛季，并且在2018年英联杯决赛上，他在球队后期的跑动表现上有着亮眼的表现。

