2018-12-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181213134640/https://www.bbc.com/sport/football/46037946|archive-date=2018-12-13|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{zh-cn}}{{cite news|title=各项赛事22场不败，阿森纳创2007年以来最长记录|url=http://dy.163.com/v2/article/detail/E30OSGO00514N8UL.html|accessdate=2018-12-14|work=网易|date=2018-12-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190525155706/http://dy.163.com/v2/article/detail/E30OSGO00514N8UL.html|archive-date=2019-05-25|dead-url=no}}</ref>在2月28日主场对阵伯恩茅斯的比赛中，厄齐尔在第四分钟首开纪录，并在第27分钟助攻姆希塔良扩大比分，帮助球队以5:1的比分大胜。<ref>{{en}}{{cite news|title=Arsenal 5-1 Bournemouth: Gunners score five to stay in top four - BBC Sport|url=https://www.bbc.com/sport/football/47301079|accessdate=2019-02-28|work=BBC sport|date=2019-02-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190227220746/https://www.bbc.com/sport/football/47301079|archive-date=2019-02-27|dead-url=no}}</ref>4月21日客场对阵[[水晶宫|水晶宫]]的比赛中，厄齐尔在第47分钟打进扳平比分的一球，但最终未能挽回败局，球队以2:3失利。<ref>{{en}}{{cite news|title=Arsenal 2-3 Crystal Palace - BBC Sport|url=https://www.bbc.com/sport/football/47924118|accessdate=2019-04-21|work=BBC sport|date=2019-04-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190422193029/https://www.bbc.com/sport/football/47924118|archive-date=2019-04-22|dead-url=no}}</ref>本赛季，厄齐尔各项赛事总计出场35次，贡献了6个进球及3个助攻。本赛季厄齐尔并不是固定的首发成员，经常以替补身份出战，甚至有时无法进入大名单，埃梅里表示他与厄齐尔并没有矛盾，并声称他依旧是队内不可或缺的一份子。<ref>{{en}}{{cite news|title=Mesut Ozil: Arsenal midfielder will be rotated, says Unai Emery|url=https://www.bbc.com/sport/football/47326263|accessdate=2019-02-21|work=BBC sport|date=2019-02-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190222084729/https://www.bbc.com/sport/football/47326263|archive-date=2019-02-22|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{en}}{{cite news|title=Arsenal need Ozil - Emery|url=https://www.bbc.com/sport/av/football/46654342|accessdate=2018-12-22|work=BBC sport|date=2018-12-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190525155704/https://www.bbc.com/sport/av/football/46654342|archive-date=2019-05-25|dead-url=no}}</ref>在欧联杯决赛[[阿森纳|阿森纳]]1:4不敌[[切尔西|切尔西]]的比赛中，厄齐尔首发出场，在下半场比分落后的时候被替换。<ref>{{en}}{{cite news|title=Mesut Ozil allegedly told Arsenal manager Unai Emery ‘you are not a coach’ in 4-1 mauling by Chelsea in Europa League final|url=https://talksport.com/football/552642/mesut-ozil-arsenal-unai-emery-2/|accessdate=2019-06-03|work=talk SPORT|date=2019-06-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190604005257/https://talksport.com/football/552642/mesut-ozil-arsenal-unai-emery-2/|archive-date=2019-06-04|dead-url=no}}</ref>北京时间6月7日，厄齐尔在Instagram上宣布自己将于当地时间明天与女友古尔西结婚。他在Instagram上写道，“众多亲朋好友都向我们送上新婚祝福。作为一名职业球员，我很幸运。但是我想请所有人为一项特殊项目提供帮助，古尔西和我将为1000名需要进行手术的孩子们提供帮助。”<ref>{{en}}{{cite news|title=Mesut Ozil: Arsenal midfielder and fiancee to fund surgery for 1,000  children|url=https://www.bbc.com/sport/football/48554743|accessdate=2019-06-07|work=BBC sport|date=2019-06-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190730131237/https://www.bbc.com/sport/football/48554743|archive-date=2019-07-30|dead-url=no}}</ref>6月8日，二人在伊斯坦布尔举行婚礼，土耳其总统[[埃尔多安|埃尔多安]]担任证婚人。<ref>{{en}}{{cite news|title=Turkey's Erdogan is best man at footballer Mesut Ozil's wedding|url=https://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-48564192|accessdate=2019-06-07|work=BBC sport|date=2019-06-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190607223523/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-48564192|archive-date=2019-06-07|dead-url=no}}</ref>

====2019-20赛季====
因2019年7月的遭抢劫未遂事件，厄齐尔直到2019年9月15日对阵[[沃特福德足球俱乐部|沃特福德]]的比赛中才上演了赛季首秀。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/49624219|title=Arsenal 2–2 Watford|website=BBC Sport|access-date=5 October 2019|archive-date=2021-01-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210120234827/https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/49624219|dead-url=no}}</ref>本赛季厄齐尔的出场机会依旧不多，直到11月份才重返首发阵容。

2019年12月，厄齊爾针对新疆再教育营在社交媒體上發帖，稱維吾爾族人為「抵抗壓迫的戰士」，同時批評中國以及對此沉默的穆斯林群體。阿森納俱樂部與厄齊爾的言論劃清界線，表示俱樂部「作為一家足球俱樂部一貫堅持不涉及政治的原因」。 在他的帖文發佈後，厄齊爾在中國版的[[实况足球2020|实况足球2020]]遊戲當中角色被刪除，球隊此後與曼城的比賽原本要在官方中央電視台播放，亦被取消。

2020年2月16日阿森纳4-0战胜[[纽卡斯尔联|纽卡斯尔联]]的比赛中，他打进了本赛季唯一的进球。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/51431286|title=Arsenal picked up just their seventh Premier League victory of the season with a confidence-boosting thrashing of Newcastle at Emirates Stadium|publisher=BBC Sport|access-date=16 February 2020|archive-date=2020-10-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201021023524/https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/51431286|dead-url=no}}</ref>此后由于[[COVID-19|COVID-19]]疫情爆发，英超暂停数月之久；英超复赛后，厄齐尔再未获得上场机会。

====2020-21赛季====
由于表现不佳，本赛季厄齐尔几乎遭到阿森纳弃用。厄齐尔被排除在2020-21赛季球队的英超及[[欧联杯|欧联杯]]大名单之外，这意味着他只能为阿森纳U-23效力。<ref>{{Cite news|last=Ames|first=Nick|date=8 October 2020|title=Mesut Özil looks to have played last Arsenal game after European omission|language=en-GB|work=The Guardian|url=https://www.theguardian.com/football/2020/oct/08/mesut-ozil-left-out-of-arsenals-25-man-europa-league-squad|access-date=8 October 2020|issn=0261-3077|archive-date=2021-01-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210125143041/https://www.theguardian.com/football/2020/oct/08/mesut-ozil-left-out-of-arsenals-25-man-europa-league-squad|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url = https://www.beinsports.com/us/premier-league/video/ozil-omitted-from-arsenals-premier-league-sq/1567329 | title = Ozil Omitted From Arsenal's Premier League Squad | website = beinsports.com | date = 21 October 2020 | access-date = 21 October 2020 | archive-date = 2020-11-30 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201130002025/https://www.beinsports.com/us/premier-league/video/ozil-omitted-from-arsenals-premier-league-sq/1567329 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|title='I failed with Ozil' - Arteta|language=en-GB|work=BBC Sport|url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/54631791|access-date=21 October 2020|archive-date=2021-01-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210124185735/https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/54631791|dead-url=no}}</ref>对此厄齐尔在社交媒体上表示自己“深感失望”，但会“继续为（自己的）机会而战”。<ref>{{Cite tweet |user=mesutozil1088 |title=This is a difficult message to write to the Arsenal fans that I've played for over the past few years |number=1318874490646953984 |date=21 October 2020 }}</ref>

