助攻<ref>{{en}}{{cite web |url=https://twitter.com/OptaJoe/status/657969575758274561 |title=2.71 – Mesut Özil has the best games/assist rate in @PremierLeague history – average one every 2.71 matches. (min. 20 assists) Provider. |author=OptaJoe |date=2015-10-24 |access-date=2015-10-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307120107/https://twitter.com/OptaJoe/status/657969575758274561 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。德國U21領隊[[霍斯特·赫鲁贝施|-{zh-cn:赫鲁贝施;zh-hk:賀巴殊;zh-tw:赫魯貝施;}-]]曾表示：「國內人民大肆吹捧外國球員，如英格蘭的[[朗尼|朗尼]]、[[基斯坦奴·朗拿度|基斯坦奴·朗拿度]]和[[美斯|美斯]]等。但我們國家（德國）有着自己的美斯，而他便是奧斯爾。」<ref>{{en}}{{cite web|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/sport/worldcup2010/article-1289196/WORLD-CUP-2010-England-end-Messi-control-Germany-star-Mesut-Ozil.html|title=WORLD CUP 2010: England will end up in a Messi if they can't control Germany star Mesut Ozil|publisher=dailymail.co.uk|date=2010-06-24|accessdate=2010-11-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303214252/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/sport/worldcup2010/article-1289196/WORLD-CUP-2010-England-end-Messi-control-Germany-star-Mesut-Ozil.html|archive-date=2016-03-03|dead-url=no}}</ref>。於2012年歐國盃對陣[[比利時國家足球隊|比利時]]時，奧斯爾射入一球，被形容為「像藝術品一樣」<ref>{{de}}{{cite web|url=http://derstandard.at/1317020071820/Hiddink-verflucht-Oezil-gefeiert|title=Hiddink verflucht, Özil gefeiert|publisher=derstandard.at|date=2011-10-12|accessdate=2011-10-19|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120116114713/http://derstandard.at/1317020071820/Hiddink-verflucht-Oezil-gefeiert|archivedate=2012-01-16|dead-url=no}}</ref>。領隊[[路維|路維]]表示他是天才，並稱讚他的無球跑動<ref>{{en}}{{cite web|url=http://www.goal.com/de/news/829/dfb-team/2011/02/10/2346567/trotz-genialer-momente-entt%C3%A4uschung-bei-mesut-%C3%B6zil-und-lukas|title=Trotz "genialer Momente": Enttäuschung bei Mesut Özil und Lukas Podolski|language=de|publisher=Goal.com|date=2011-02-10|accessdate=2011-10-19|last=Duchateau|first=Francois|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110214000607/http://www.goal.com/de/news/829/dfb-team/2011/02/10/2346567/trotz-genialer-momente-entt%C3%A4uschung-bei-mesut-%C3%B6zil-und-lukas|archive-date=2011-02-14|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

