/20150405044940/http://www.goal.com/en/news/1717/editorial/2013/04/09/3886081/i-will-always-be-turkish-why-ozil-is-worshipped-in-istanbul | archive-date = 2015-04-05 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{tr}}{{cite web|url=http://www.sabah.com.tr/Spor/2010/06/27/mesut_ozilin_hayali_barca|title=Mesut Özil'in hayali Barça|publisher=Sabah|date=2010-06-27|accessdate=2010-06-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141219131918/http://www.sabah.com.tr/spor/2010/06/27/mesut_ozilin_hayali_barca|archive-date=2014-12-19|dead-url=no}}</ref>。但仍有報導聲稱奧斯爾的祖先為[[庫爾德|庫爾德]]族人<ref>{{en}}{{cite web | url=http://worldsoccer.about.com/od/players/p/Mesut-Ozil.htm | title=Mesut Ozil Profile | publisher=worldsoccer.about.com | accessdate=2014-11-20 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141201233333/http://worldsoccer.about.com/od/players/p/Mesut-Ozil.htm | archive-date=2014-12-01 | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{tr}}{{cite web|url=http://www.hurriyet.com.tr/spor/futbol/15319147.asp?gid=373|title=Mesut Barzani'den Mesut Özil'e davet|work=hurriyet.com.tr|date=2010-07-15|accessdate=2015-02-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141028140429/http://www.hurriyet.com.tr/spor/futbol/15319147.asp?gid=373|archive-date=2014-10-28|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

